ygData.messageBody:
Yeah, my buddy Larn left me in the dust for level. Damn him!!!!! Its ok, now
I get to the be the resident puller of SOL B for the groups camping assorted
areas. I am getting to learn Sol B quite well now, quick question though,
the start of the room with the sonic bats hovering, is there only one or are
they stacked upon on another so as you can not see them all or what? I don't
want a nasty surprise if I try to pull these to my group.
